---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Hero from '@components/Hero.astro'
import '../styles/global.css'
---

<Layout title='About'>
  <Hero title='About' image='/images/about-page-cover.jpg' alt='About page Cover Image' />
  <section id='about-content' class='md:flex w-full px-4 lg:px-12 py-12'>
    <div id='about-illustration' class='md:w-1/2 my-8 md:my-0 flex items-center justify-center'>
      <img src='/images/arun.jpg' alt='About page illustration' class="w-full max-w-[300px] h-auto aspect-square object-cover rounded-full shadow border-4 border-gray-100"/>
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:my-auto">
      <h2 id="about-title" class='text-2xl font-bold text-center text-slate-700'>Who I am ?</h2>
      <p class="my-4 md:mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        I'm Arun, a writer, editor, researcher, and actor based in Bengaluru,
        India. My background is in the social sciences: I hold a BA in Social
        Sciences and Humanities and an MSc in Applied Linguistics, and for the
        past five years I've been working as a freelancer, primarily in the
        education sector and academia. In my work and in my life, I try to put
        the journey before the destination, focusing on long-term growth rather

        than short-term gratification. 
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">As a writing coach, I invite you to look
        closely at your own life and tell your own stories in your own words,
        without relying on anyone else to do it for you—not even AI. If you'd
        like to see more of what I do, you can find me on Instagram, Substack,
        and LinkedIn. For a detailed look at my experience and qualifications,
        you can also browse my CV.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="border-b border-gray-200 w-1/2 mb-8 mx-auto"></div>
  <section class="lg:px-12 md:px-8 px-4 pb-16">
    <h2 class='text-2xl font-bold text-center text-slate-700 mb-8'>My Story</h2>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
        My work experience — in India and the UK — has primarily been in the fields of education and research. I have received PhD offers from SOAS University of London, Queen Mary University of London, and Manchester Metropolitan University, as well as been nominated for three prestigious PhD studentships: <a href="https://www.lahp.ac.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 underline font-semibold">LAHP-DTP</a>, <a href="https://liss-dtp.ac.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 underline font-semibold">LISS-DTP</a>, and the <a href="https://www.qmul.ac.uk/postgraduate/research/funding_phd/studentships" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 underline font-semibold">QM Principal Studentship</a>. Two of my works have been published in academic journals: an <a href="https://journals.plos.org/ploscompbiol/article?id=10.1371/journal.pcbi.1011797" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 underline font-semibold">article on inclusivity at academic conferences</a> and a <a href="https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/15505170.2024.2380324" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 underline font-semibold">review of the current research in raciolinguistics</a>. I am a member of the <a href="https://www.baal.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 underline font-semibold">British Association for Applied Linguistics</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
        When I'm not working to help my clients polish their research or improve the quality of their writing, I'm usually running, reading, composing music, or playing RTS games on PC.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
        You can find me on <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/arunlinguist" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 underline font-semibold">LinkedIn</a>, <a href="http://instagram.com/linguistarun" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 underline font-semibold">Instagram</a>, <a href="https://substack.com/@thearunrams" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 underline font-semibold">Substack</a>, and <a href="https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4994-5294" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 underline font-semibold">ORCID</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
